{"id": 2777, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今哪些「群聊礼仪」已经是你的习惯动作了？", "description": "不同于一对一聊天，「如何在群聊中表现得人见人爱」是一门学问。（题图来自：iStock ©️ jossdim）", "record_count": 12057, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2019021115501161TXlwAKhaCdP3kj.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-02-14T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5355, "title": "现如今哪些「群聊礼仪」已经是你的习惯动作了？", "content": "说到“当代群聊礼仪”，你都有哪些心得？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 326912, "content": "人很多的群聊，进群之后先改一下群昵称", "image": "img/option/option/20190211172124PSV8kcEMTwyfUO2s.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 326892, "content": "拉群之前尽量先通知别人", "image": "img/option/option/20190211172322fJpbhBWjMlwYiTC6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 326894, "content": "在群里转发拉票求赞之类的帖子，先发个红包", "image": "img/option/option/2019021117231057VHyXW3mL1Fzv6a.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 326896, "content": "单独开一个群转发购物红包/小游戏链接", "image": "img/option/option/20190212135332Jr6Xn9AhBliK0f25.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 326902, "content": "需要找群里的某个人帮忙，可以先@再私聊", "image": "img/option/option/20190211172206FZ154ELqT2GnhpDC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 326904, "content": "不在人很多的群里发超大文件和视频", "image": "img/option/option/20190211172421KUtQ6nEeBjpOSFZq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 326909, "content": "尽量不在群里发语音", "image": "img/option/option/201902111721494Pkdvg2fZFItAjwY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 326910, "content": "能一条消息讲完就不用两条，帮大家节约眼神", "image": "img/option/option/201902111721367Jpm1MzHQueivjZ8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}